descriptionHtml:
I made a custom profile for the FXAA Injector and decided to upload it for everyone to use.
Makes the game look more natural and suits the theme of the location.

Install: Unzip in your Skyrim root dir, make sure you have FXAA Injector.

Grab the FXAA Injector here (http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=131)


***please note the .h file included in this isnt compatible with the FXAA injector linked here (the newest version)
To make it work  add a \"1\" (without quotes) to each #define line, and it will work---only if your using the new version. adding the 1 to the end of the lines.
Thanks for pointing this out moriz

All credit goes to the modder who created the injector -some_dude

I will also include the config file i am using which increases view distance and shadow detail and water resolution.

Please also note you will need a powerful rig to run this.

Video now up:)
http://youtu.be/cuogT_dmHe8

Thanks
